data.description: Short-Sale! Split Level Home, with partially finished basement is within walking distance to LHU! This adorable split level home features 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, PLUS a bonus space in the lower level are perfect for older children or could easily to be converted into ''in-law'' quarters w/ a kitchenette space. Needs some love, but has potential to be beautiful. Hardwood flooring in several rooms needs refinished, a mini-split heat pump / central air system (kitchen, living room, dining room). Off-street parking located in the rear.   Adjacent from Hanna Park & Susquehanna River providing 4 seasons of mountainous views. Recent fall-through due to lengthy short sale process.  Short Sale initiated in July 2023.
